      "content": "Right, so if we follow that logic, then any regulation—whether it's for content moderation or data privacy—is basically just a government infringement on that digital agora. Do you think most people realize how much their fundamental rights are being eroded by these regulations, or is the argument for regulation actually just a way for governments to maintain control?",
